# NOTE: this endpoint is also published to the public internet via Tailscale
# Funnel (https://tj-lt.tail34a5cf.ts.net:8443/, TUE-55). The basic-auth
# credential below is the ONLY gate, so the plaintext is deliberately NOT
# stored in git — it is delivered to Jonas via the Paperclip issue thread.
# Rotate with:
#   docker run --rm caddy:2 caddy hash-password --plaintext '<new-password>'
#   then replace the hash below and `docker compose restart caddy`.
